R2WinBUGS-package       Running WinBUGS and OpenBUGS from R / S-PLUS
as.bugs.array           Convert to bugs object
attach.all              Attach / detach elements of (bugs) objects to
                        search path
bugs                    Run WinBUGS and OpenBUGS from R or S-PLUS
bugs.log                Read data from WinBUGS logfile
openbugs                Wrapper to run OpenBUGS
plot.bugs               Plotting a bugs object
print.bugs              Printing a bugs object
read.bugs               Read output files in CODA format
schools                 8 schools analysis
write.model             Creating a WinBUGS model file
